<ab facs="#facs_101_r1l29"><expan>berg<ex>er</ex></expan> / do er vns vormals von <expan>ſeine<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> / auch <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat mıt <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_102" id="50r"/>
<ab facs="#facs_102_r1l1">brıef <expan>vnd<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>dıng<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> / vvıe <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> Neẅmeır dıe weıl er <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_102_r1l2">was . von ſeinr vntat <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> bey vns ʒu fenknuſſ kam / Darinn er <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>gnedıg<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_102_r1l3"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>cʒog</expan> <expan>heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Peyern vnd <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>gute<ex>n</ex></expan> freẅnd . des Rats der Stat ʒu </ab>
