<ab facs="#facs_102_r1l7">als <expan>ſölıch<ex>er</ex></expan> brıef <expan>abſchrıfte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>hıerynn<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſloſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>clerlıch<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>auſʒweıſe<ex>n</ex></expan> / VVıl nu <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> </ab>
