<ab facs="#facs_102_r1l13"><expan>ſein<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>vord<ex>er</ex>n</expan> brıef <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . keıns ends <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſtünde</expan> etc / Nu <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır Jm in <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> </ab>
